Features Enabled Documentation
# Features Enabled

Full strict mode

Catches:
- null/undefined usage
- unsafe any
- unsafe function types
- uninitialized class properties

Path aliases  
Required for clean imports like:  

import { UserService } from "@/modules/user/services/user.service";
